-- Clemens Accuser Says Ex-Pitcher Sought Help With Steroid Shot
-- B y   T o m   S c h o e n b e r g
-- 2012-05-14T18:37:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-14/clemens-accuser-says-ex-pitcher-sought-help-with-steroid-shot.html
Ex-New York Yankees pitcher  Roger
Clemens  asked for help with administering a shot of anabolic
steroids, his former trainer, Brian McNamee, testified today in
federal court in Washington.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tom Schoenberg in Washington at 
